* Again, the female fuzor found herself awake, the vibrations actually turning out to be voices of...male bots?
She slowly began to lift her head but this time her neck was far too sore and she let it drop again, hunger causing her stomach to growl and ache.
Now with the instincts of her beast modes she was also following their feeding habbits.
The smell of the two male's mech-fluid reaching her systems and causing her stomach to growl again, her systems only feeding on the blood of animals or that fluid of bots. Either worked.
But without repair she couldn't do anything, so, she simply stayed there. Being tossed back and forth by two male bots in which she did not know.
It was almost as if they were fighting over her, for some reason or another.
It really didn't matter, either one was warm and she was cold, her shivers increasing.
As Bloodystrike pulled her towards him she tried to  move closer to him for his heat, trying to warm herself.And actually succeeding.
She tried to do the same when she was pulled towards Reptilica, actually managing to lean against him and draw a bit of his warmth into her body as well.
Her shivers had increased but they hadn't gotten any worse.*
